[
    {
        "text": "When I was twelve years old,...",
        "startTime": 2923,
        "endTime": 4508,
        "slowStartTime": 4534,
        "slowEndTime": 6987
    },
    {
        "text": "...someone put my first bat in my hand.",
        "startTime": 4667,
        "endTime": 7043,
        "slowStartTime": 7150,
        "slowEndTime": 10790
    },
    {
        "text": "That sealed my fate.",
        "startTime": 7975,
        "endTime": 9835,
        "slowStartTime": 12112,
        "slowEndTime": 14978
    },
    {
        "text": "Bats are the most unfairly treated animals on Earth.",
        "startTime": 16113,
        "endTime": 20643,
        "slowStartTime": 24320,
        "slowEndTime": 31189
    },
    {
        "text": "Fear, not knowing what treasure they have in their local cave,...",
        "startTime": 21721,
        "endTime": 26339,
        "slowStartTime": 32732,
        "slowEndTime": 39734
    },
    {
        "text": "...drives people to dynamite it, to gas them, to all kinds of things.",
        "startTime": 26628,
        "endTime": 32544,
        "slowStartTime": 40092,
        "slowEndTime": 49041
    },
    {
        "text": "But bats provide us with many ecosystem services, agricultural pest control.",
        "startTime": 33401,
        "endTime": 39375,
        "slowStartTime": 50252,
        "slowEndTime": 59287
    },
    {
        "text": "Each million bats destroy ten tons of insects every night.",
        "startTime": 42344,
        "endTime": 47138,
        "slowStartTime": 63666,
        "slowEndTime": 70932
    },
    {
        "text": "If we lose those bats, we would lose the crops in a few months.",
        "startTime": 48347,
        "endTime": 52547,
        "slowStartTime": 72670,
        "slowEndTime": 79046
    },
    {
        "text": "They're also promoting the regeneration of the forest...",
        "startTime": 55127,
        "endTime": 57698,
        "slowStartTime": 82840,
        "slowEndTime": 86772
    },
    {
        "text": "...by dispersing the seeds over vast, vast areas,...",
        "startTime": 58069,
        "endTime": 60865,
        "slowStartTime": 87253,
        "slowEndTime": 91522
    },
    {
        "text": "...and they pollinate...",
        "startTime": 63034,
        "endTime": 63994,
        "slowStartTime": 94701,
        "slowEndTime": 96216
    },
    {
        "text": "...a lot of ecologically or economically important species of plants...",
        "startTime": 64455,
        "endTime": 69437,
        "slowStartTime": 96833,
        "slowEndTime": 104380
    },
    {
        "text": "...like the agaves that are the source for tequila,...",
        "startTime": 69645,
        "endTime": 73547,
        "slowStartTime": 104618,
        "slowEndTime": 110545
    },
    {
        "text": "...which represents for Mexico about three billion dollars a year.",
        "startTime": 74194,
        "endTime": 78737,
        "slowStartTime": 111441,
        "slowEndTime": 118331
    },
    {
        "text": "We created a humongous network...",
        "startTime": 79354,
        "endTime": 82111,
        "slowStartTime": 119181,
        "slowEndTime": 123391
    },
    {
        "text": "...of privately owned protected areas around the country...",
        "startTime": 82519,
        "endTime": 86173,
        "slowStartTime": 123929,
        "slowEndTime": 129485
    },
    {
        "text": "...that today includes about 17% of Mexico's territory.",
        "startTime": 86325,
        "endTime": 91098,
        "slowStartTime": 129637,
        "slowEndTime": 136872
    },
    {
        "text": "When I have a bat in my hand and I show it to anybody,...",
        "startTime": 93353,
        "endTime": 96707,
        "slowStartTime": 140179,
        "slowEndTime": 145286
    },
    {
        "text": "...you see the change in a flash.",
        "startTime": 97157,
        "endTime": 99609,
        "slowStartTime": 145886,
        "slowEndTime": 149638
    },
    {
        "text": "This is exactly what has been driving me for a long, long time.",
        "startTime": 100401,
        "endTime": 104863,
        "slowStartTime": 150751,
        "slowEndTime": 157519
    },
    {
        "text": "I am here, at 64, continue to be the same child...",
        "startTime": 105527,
        "endTime": 110777,
        "slowStartTime": 158440,
        "slowEndTime": 166391
    },
    {
        "text": "...who had his first bat in his hand.",
        "startTime": 110867,
        "endTime": 112837,
        "slowStartTime": 166450,
        "slowEndTime": 169481
    },
    {
        "text": "I will never give up.",
        "startTime": 113248,
        "endTime": 114945,
        "slowStartTime": 170022,
        "slowEndTime": 172643
    }
]